</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FBD52B85C63C582B9458D338096A1AC6" pageId="null" pageNumber="580" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="FD919001B52B394D55EB90643FB51CE1" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Unvergleichliche Narzisse</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="6E5A3ACF8005289BC4A994FEEF7DD693" pageId="null" pageNumber="580" type="description">
<paragraph id="201A29136E538B633ED441143789E24B" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="22A3DD3D5257171705C210F21237D9F2" class="Liliopsida" family="Amaryllidaceae" genus="Narcissus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="580" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pseudonarcissus">
<emphasis id="887246E8205F00A6E51705E8338A7088" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">N. Pseudonarcissus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1) im wesentlichen nur durch das folgende Merkmal: 
<emphasis id="C5C30682720648FF02B3FD447FEFD003" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Nebenkrone etwa</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="208F4F0F451D3500CE99BBE96CEEBAC0" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="135BD2AEC340D335E95B035FAE84C823" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">so lang wie die freien Perigonzipfel.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="181358CDC43F8E1E5ED61B4B8CE7B425" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="0B4DD7180AE42DF9C244D8981FDB21F5" originalValue="Früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Frueher</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="3B9C289CF0D159298FF551D375EC61F7" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="43EDC8AF535E96CAB8311E7D5F2DC3A9" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">
<emphasis id="0306498B18C9130A5E1235532C50BC54" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">
<pageBreakToken id="5D9D98B19221E94AA4633BCC3432B387" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Zytologische</pageBreakToken>
Angaben. 2n
</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="FBA9858753AA842FD9C05F585B3696BF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">14, 21:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="DCE168C1DAB8B82174949F1129116DC0" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Sikka 1940); nach Fernandes (1942) soll 
<taxonomicName id="73843D867D3798D616B4C2F532CE097A" class="Liliopsida" family="Amaryllidaceae" genus="Narcissus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="580" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="incomparabilis">
<emphasis id="EFE6F768AC5EAEF03FA01BDDC0368F87" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">N. incomparabilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
als reine Art existieren, zudem soll es auch Bastarde zwischen 
<taxonomicName id="8A5D6298893F1ED66BB58DB29CEF1498" class="Liliopsida" family="Amaryllidaceae" genus="Narcissus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="580" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pseudonarcissus">
<emphasis id="E47F65F3273786381DE653AEF6ECB062" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">N. Pseudonarcissus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="0DD910D49D77D1F6B8AE649F050475D8" class="Liliopsida" family="Amaryllidaceae" genus="Narcissus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="580" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="poeticus">
<emphasis id="539078B9361612551A5F5B73F1D682CD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">N. poeticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
geben, die sich nicht von 
<taxonomicName id="C5840D379E735FC0A8014E903045EA45" class="Liliopsida" family="Amaryllidaceae" genus="Narcissus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="null" pageNumber="580" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="incomparabilis">
<emphasis id="46F8B2C5F9D93673D1620EB6F0349516" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">N. incomparabilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
unterscheiden lassen. 
<emphasis id="13CFA7591CA34BDB2008DC74E34F5498" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="DEE1EDE10358C4879224C169E3054B86" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">28:</emphasis>
(Takenaka aus 
<normalizedToken id="10FEC00FCE76DDE859C860DA5209815D" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="3B92500928EC935017E6415A44F3ECC5" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1961).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8514F5EC047F81E351E4479096DD81E1" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">
<emphasis id="B0A9BF3E048353602FDA58491019D98B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Wiesen. Verwilderte Gartenpflanze.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="65A538ACC4BD440B88B2DE70AE4BD6DD" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">
<emphasis id="86D134C4674DEC18E0BD3F9FEE9D488C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="BCA9447B79EE514A4691204AB3C6E3EC" originalValue="Ungenügend" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Ungenuegend</normalizedToken>
bekannt; 
<normalizedToken id="D0EB90B64FFC69C1E921B6D0031C1FB0" originalValue="südfranzösische" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">suedfranzoesische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze.
</emphasis>
- Im Gebiet am 
<normalizedToken id="1D39C62463FBA522D97252F15CF264BC" originalValue="Alpensüdfuß" pageId="null" pageNumber="580">Alpensuedfuss</normalizedToken>
gelegentlich verwildert.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
